overrideValues.value: When time is of essence, and your health requires immediate attention, Criti Care takes away your financial worries. It gives you instant cash to cover expensive medical bills or compensate a loss of income due to sickness from 32 covered diseases. Criti care also featured with a 75% return of the premiums and an Excess Interest Bonus (EIB) at maturity.
